data.description: Meticulously upgraded Home in the exclusive Gated Community of Monarch Lakes. Move-in ready, open concept, tall ceilings w/very spacious floor plan & tons of Natural Light! Totally updated w/Neutral-Modern Design: Gourmet Kitchen w/GE Profile SS Appl, upgraded countertops, backsplash & hood. Master suite w/large bath & Walk-in Closet. The remaining 3 beds have plenty of space, laminated wood floors & nicely done baths. Laundry on the hall w/Upgraded Samsung top load washer & dryer. Enjoy relaxing or entertaining outdoors from your extended covered patio & fully fenced yard. Complete Hurricane Protection w/Impact windows: Front & Patio doors, Zebra shades, Fans, Modern light fixture & more! Updated playground, basketball & tennis courts. Close to shopping, restaurants, Hospitals & Others!
